<br>
Aggro *can* be so wacky as is that to claim anything off one experience - even one experience from a few different people is just plain wrong. If 5k casters play tonight and cast 200 nukes each that's a million nukes .. *some* are gonna cause the mob to turn on the caster for no obvious reason and some people *are* gonna die when they never did before whether any nerf has happened or not; it's just simple statistics I'm afraid. It's amplified on message boards because people are far more likely to post 'that happened to me too!' posts than 'err.. that didnt happen to me' ones.<br>
